## Additional Terms for Educational Use

This repository contains educational materials for the M110 Python Programming
course at Arab Open University, Amman Branch.

### For Students:
- You are free to use, study, and modify these materials for learning purposes
- You may share your solutions and projects, but please respect academic integrity
- When sharing derived work, please attribute the original source

### For Educators:
- You are welcome to use and adapt these materials for your own courses
- Please provide attribution to the original author (Mohammad Al-Marie)
- If you make improvements, consider sharing them back with the community

### For the Community:
- Contributions are welcome via pull requests
- Please maintain the educational and beginner-friendly nature of the materials
- Keep all content appropriate for academic settings
